{
  "stem": "27129.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So this is how he survived.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So he got to know a girl over there, and they got married later on.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was Maged was the other, the other woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "She was from Lithuania, that woman.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when we wrote to them, you know, he found out where we are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He got our address.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "After the release from the labor camp, he came to us with his wife.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The camp was in, in, in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now they call it the old name, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he came to us over there to [NON-ENGLISH], and he worked as a barber.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in the meantime, we were already-- no, not to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He came to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He came to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Later, he was, he was in, in that camp inducted.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then he found out where we are in [NON-ENGLISH], so then he came to [NON-ENGLISH], and he worked as a barber, too.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So in the-- he, well, he had-- in the meantime, he had a child with that, with that woman.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So he was-- it was a little bit different for him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But with this woman, this woman was the first wife he had a child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I'm mixing up a little bit.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "With his first wife, he had a child, before he got inducted.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So then he got to know this woman, and he got married with her, and he came to us to [NON-ENGLISH] also.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, in Lodz we went back to Liegnitz, because the kids were in Liegnitz, in, in, Upper-- Lower Silesia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we were thinking that, uh, how to go away from Poland.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in the meantime, they were creating, organizing kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So with the kibbutz, they could go to, to Israel, which was at that time Palestine.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
